text.tspan: Before we start, we will show how users can create a proposal
and get access to the relevant services in reality.
Each students will also have their own account
to log into our virtual machine services.
DMSC is inviting anyone who is interested in our software to the 3rd DMSC summer school in Copenhagen!
As the European Spallation Source (ESS) is built in Lund, Sweden,
various software for ESS is developed in Copenhagen, Denmark at Data Management and Software Centre (DMSC).
The summer school will cover most parts of data management and software for ESS.
Studetns can choose 1 (or more) track of science case
and follow the full data pipeline
from simulation to publishing data analysis results!
See the real facility and DAQ part
